dengan pengacaraku dahulu.

525
00:36:56,589 --> 00:36:57,882
Tak apa jika kurekam?

526
00:36:59,217 --> 00:37:00,760
Aku mau meminta maaf.

527
00:37:01,886 --> 00:37:04,222
