540
00:37:49,350 --> 00:37:51,435
Dia mungkin membenci kita,

541
00:37:51,519 --> 00:37:54,480
tetapi aku yakin kau bisa membujuknya.

542
00:37:54,563 --> 00:37:57,108
Dari yang kudengar, kalian sering berjumpa

543
00:37:57,692 --> 00:37:59,235
dan sudah akrab.

544
00:38:00,695 --> 00:38:01,821
Akan kulakukan.

545
00:38:38,607 --> 00:38:40,318
Katamu bangku di dekat lampu jalan?

546
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:43,404
Ya, seingatku bangku berwarna biru.

547
00:38:44,655 --> 00:38:46,490
Bangku berwarna biru...

